The Zooop is a three-seat [[electric car]] produced by the Paris-based fashion house [[André Courrèges|Maison de Courrèges]].

The Courreges Zooop performance is 150 kW and weighing just 690 kilograms, also features a range of 450 kilometers. Remarkably, the car is not produced for a car manufacturer, but it is produced by the famous fashion design house Maison de Courrèges, which peculiarly did scarce promotion for its new model outside its native country.<ref>[https://www.motor1.com/news/90803/courreges-zooop/ Courreges Zooop]</ref>
